    public interface PsiAppendable<T extends PsiObject>
extends PsiObject
    A representation of Ψ-appendable, a type of container that allow to append Ψ objects (usually to the end, if it makes sense).

      • psiAppendAll

        default void psiAppendAll(PsiIterable<? extends T> oEnumeration)
                   throws PsiException
        Appends all the Ψ-objects from a given Ψ-iterable enumeration to this container. When a given enumeration is the same as this container, first clone the enumeration, and then appends all the elements from the clone to avoid concurrent modification.
        Parameters:
